112
00:12:29,583 --> 00:12:30,458
Hmm?

113
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:36,500
[GOKU hums]

114
00:12:36,583 --> 00:12:38,125
Lunch!

115
00:12:40,666 --> 00:12:42,083
Huh?

116
00:12:51,125 --> 00:12:54,791
I don't suppose you'd be
willing to hop in my stomach?

117
00:12:56,541 --> 00:12:57,916
[GOKU]
Didn't think so.

118
00:13:20,333 --> 00:13:22,166
[chuckles]

119
00:13:43,583 --> 00:13:45,916
Dragon Balls. Huh.

120
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:48,875
And you're telling us,
if you get all seven,

121
00:13:48,958 --> 00:13:50,875
any wish you make comes true?

122
00:13:50,958 --> 00:13:53,708
Yep, but you only get one wish.

123
00:13:53,791 --> 00:13:56,041
So obviously we
should use that wish

124
00:13:56,125 --> 00:13:58,250
to bring Krillin back to life.

125
