Well, I know this
is going to sound bad,

126
00:14:02,083 --> 00:14:05,166
but I really think we should
use the wish to defeat Piccolo.

127
00:14:05,250 --> 00:14:07,583
There's no way we
can beat him on our own.

128
00:14:07,666 --> 00:14:08,958
I know we have
to bring Krillin back,

129
00:14:09,041 --> 00:14:11,250
but that monster's unstoppable.

130
00:14:11,333 --> 00:14:13,291
Is that a good idea, Yamcha?

131
00:14:13,375 --> 00:14:15,333
I thought the Dragon Balls
turned into stone

132
00:14:15,416 --> 00:14:18,166
for a whole year after
a wish has been granted.

133
00:14:18,250 --> 00:14:20,791
Uh, yeah,
that sure is a long time

134
00:14:20,875 --> 00:14:24,625
to let Krillin's body
hang around. Isn't it?

135
00:14:24,708 --> 00:14:26,750
Ew, and what about that smell?

136
00:14:26,833 --> 00:14:30,083
Well, if you ask me the idea of
bringing him back sounds creepy.

137
00:14:30,166 --> 00:14:31,750
Maybe we should leave him alone.

138
00:14:31,833 --> 00:14:34,791
Oh, gee pals, thanks a lot.

139
00:14:35,833 --> 00:14:39,250
Well let's see, I could make a
freezer capsule to preserve him

140
00:14:39,333 --> 00:14:41,708
until we find the
Dragon Balls again.

141
00:14:41,791 --> 00:14:44,041
Maybe one for back-stabbers too.

142
00:14:44,125 --> 00:14:46,291
Hey, I was just sayin'.

143
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:48,541
Hmm...

144
00:14:48,625 --> 00:14:50,416
Pale, pale gray.

145
00:14:50,500 --> 00:14:52,958
What? Who is pale grey?

146
00:14:53,041 --> 00:14:57,083
Wait! Is this Pale Grey
a great warrior, Master?

147
