martial arts fighters--

163
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:43,333
Come here! Listen!

164
00:15:43,416 --> 00:15:46,000
[NEWS] Police are baffled as
to the motives of the killer

165
00:15:46,083 --> 00:15:48,916
and why only
martial artists are targeted.

166
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:50,833
As to the identity
of the killer,

167
00:15:50,916 --> 00:15:54,541
police are left without a clue,
save for a piece of paper found

168
00:15:54,625 --> 00:15:57,916
on each of the bodies with the
word "devil" encircled on it.

169
00:15:58,000 --> 00:15:59,041
When we return...

170
00:15:59,125 --> 00:16:00,791
Can your clothing
drive you insane?

171
00:16:00,875 --> 00:16:01,958
You might be surprised.

172
