Um, I hear flights to the
caribbean are cheap

175
00:16:09,750 --> 00:16:11,541
this time of year.

176
00:16:11,625 --> 00:16:13,500
Guys! All the
fighters are in danger!

177
00:16:13,583 --> 00:16:15,291
We've got to warn them!

178
00:16:15,375 --> 00:16:17,583
We'd have trouble contacting
them without the list.

179
00:16:17,666 --> 00:16:20,333
Besides, many
of them use aliases.

180
00:16:21,583 --> 00:16:23,541
We can't stay here
and do nothing.

181
00:16:23,625 --> 00:16:25,208
There's got to be
some way we can help.

182
00:16:25,291 --> 00:16:29,375
I'm feeling so
useless here. Come on!

183
00:16:29,458 --> 00:16:31,708
Well, you are right
about not staying here.

184
00:16:31,791 --> 00:16:34,375
We're sitting ducks
on this island.

185
00:16:34,458 --> 00:16:35,083
Bulma!

186
00:16:35,166 --> 00:16:35,958
[BULMA]
M-hmm?

187
00:16:36,041 --> 00:16:37,083
How long would it take you

188
00:16:37,166 --> 00:16:39,375
to construct another
Dragon Ball Radar?

189
00:16:39,458 --> 00:16:40,625
[BULMA] Hmm...

190
00:16:40,708 --> 00:16:43,333
