I gotta eat something.

203
00:18:09,375 --> 00:18:13,208
[sniffs]

204
00:18:13,291 --> 00:18:17,458
Ah ha! Something smells good!
Something smells great!

205
00:18:33,250 --> 00:18:35,916
[GOKU]
It's beautiful.

206
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:38,166
Luuunch!

207
00:18:50,625 --> 00:18:51,541
[chuckles]

208
00:18:51,625 --> 00:18:53,541
Now, it's lunchtime!

209
00:19:11,500 --> 00:19:13,333
[GOKU]
Oh, yeah!

210
00:19:21,833 --> 00:19:24,250
[CYMBAL thinking]
It is near.

211
00:19:36,875 --> 00:19:39,583
[GOKU sighs]

212
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:43,875
Mmhmm!

213
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:48,208
[chuckles]

214
00:20:11,625 --> 00:20:13,666
I'm back to full strength!

215
00:20:16,166 --> 00:20:18,583
[GOKU] And now I'm
coming for you Tambourine!

216
00:20:18,666 --> 00:20:20,208
You hear me?!

217
00:20:20,291 --> 00:20:22,250
You're mine!!

218
00:20:24,583 --> 00:20:26,875
I promise you!

219
00:20:26,958 --> 00:20:29,708
Krillin will be revenged!!

220
00:20:33,041 --> 00:20:36,750
Krillin, I am so sorry
I wasn't there to stop him.

221
00:20:36,833 --> 00:20:38,666
Please forgive me.

222
00:20:41,125 --> 00:20:44,666
Now I remember!
He destroyed the Nimbus cloud!

223
00:20:50,666 --> 00:20:53,666
Ah! Oh no, what have you done?!

224
00:20:53,750 --> 00:20:55,125
Ah!!

225
00:21:01,125 --> 00:21:03,291
I'll tear that monster apart!

226
00:21:06,583 --> 00:21:08,458
Hide while you can, Tambourine!

227
00:21:08,541 --> 00:21:10,000
You're going to pay
for what you've done to

228
00:21:10,083 --> 00:21:12,083
Krillin and Nimbus!

229
00:21:12,958 --> 00:21:16,208
You think you got away,
but you took my Dragon Ball.

230
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:20,541
Ha! And with
Bulma's Dragon Ball Radar

231
00:21:20,625 --> 00:21:22,791
I know just where to find you!

232
00:21:24,958 --> 00:21:26,333
Uh...

233
00:21:29,250 --> 00:21:32,500
Huh? Is this right?

234
00:21:32,583 --> 00:21:34,000
I can't believe it!

235
00:21:34,083 --> 00:21:36,541
Tambourine's right
around here somewhere!

236
00:21:36,625 --> 00:21:39,625
Okay! Where are you? Come out!

237
00:21:56,458 --> 00:21:57,583
Hmmm?

238
00:22:11,916 --> 00:22:13,250
[GOKU]
I know you're there!

239
00:22:13,333 --> 00:22:15,916
Come out and face me you coward!

240
00:22:24,708 --> 00:22:26,250
I'm not a coward!

241
00:22:26,333 --> 00:22:28,458
You're the sneak
that stole my food!

242
00:22:28,541 --> 00:22:30,000
Huh?

243
00:22:30,083 --> 00:22:31,583
That's right!

244
00:22:31,666 --> 00:22:34,875
That fish was my dinner,
and you ate it!

245
00:22:34,958 --> 00:22:36,791
But somebody left it.

246
00:22:36,875 --> 00:22:39,208
There! On that stick!

247
00:22:39,291 --> 00:22:43,500
Oh, man! I was cooking
it on that stick, you idiot!

248
00:22:43,583 --> 00:22:44,875
[GOKU] Hmm?

249
00:22:44,958 --> 00:22:46,875
[NARRATOR] Out of the
fish fry and into the fire!

250
00:22:46,958 --> 00:22:50,166
Is this strange mountain
man friend or foe?

251
00:22:50,250 --> 00:22:54,041
Find out on the next exciting
episode of Dragon Ball!

